pull_request.title: BIKE-1 code update
pull_request.body:
This PR includes the latest code of BIKE.

1) It solves https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/issues/636 (See the same change in  https://github.com/awslabs/s2n/pull/1527/commits/affc647a5d9b3e89cb2c6a57d0b0f0c10066a488)
2) It uses short license headers
3) Some formatting changes that happen due to applying `astyle` on the latest code instead of applying clang-format as before.

pull_request.title: Updated SIKE implementation with latest changes.
pull_request.body:
This PR includes:
- Optimizations changes from PR #558, adapted to cmake
- New changes from the [SIDH library](https://github.com/microsoft/PQCrypto-SIDH), moving from commit [ebd1c8](https://github.com/microsoft/PQCrypto-SIDH/commit/ebd1c80a8ac35e9ca2ef9680291a8a43b95a3bfa) to [fde210](https://github.com/microsoft/PQCrypto-SIDH/commit/fde210a7cf03e835cceb1d5ff34ccf58625d0311).
